[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "着いたぞ。見て分かる通り、ここが――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01611",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ボスがしゃべってる途中なのに、失礼な雷です！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01612",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "自然現象に無理言っちゃダメだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01613",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "『避雷のペンダント』は肌身離さず\n持っていてくださいね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01614",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "なかなかよい意匠ですこと。\n普段使いしても良さそうですわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_036_01615",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "なぁジェロンさん、俺らには綺麗すぎて\nちょっと似合わなそうだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01616",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "そうだな。ティムはともかく……\nだがこれも落雷対策だ、仕方あるまい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_01617",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "対策しているとはいえ、危険なのは変わりない。\n皆、気を付けて進むように",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01618",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "おお、うるさいうるさい。\nどうせなら耳栓も用意してくればよかったね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_01619",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ハイディとジョゼは遊撃隊ね。\n状況を判断して好きに動いてちょうだい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01620",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ああ。俺は単独行動に慣れてるしね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01621",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "私は何かあったときのために船で待機している。\nタイニー、現場は任せたぞ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01622",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "はっ！　お任せください！\nボスの分まで、しっかり頑張ります！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01623",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "配置、逆のほうがいい気もするんだけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01624",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "邪知に長けた罠があるかもしれません。\nどんと構えた方が一人後詰めにいると、心強いので",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01625",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "経験を活かして、的確に動いてみせよう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01626",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "ほら、仮面くん。私たちは別行動だよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_01627",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そういえば雷って、どこに落ちるのかしら",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01628",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "高い所とか、大きな金属に落ちやすいんですよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_01629",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "さすがティム、詳しいな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_01630",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ふーん、じゃあこうしてみたら……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01631",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ビ、ビビッた……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01632",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ちょっとお前さん、大丈夫かい！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_01633",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "え、ええ……\n『避雷のペンダント』のおかげね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01634",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "実験で効果があるのは確認してるけど、\n実際の雷相手にどれくらい持つか分からないから……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01635",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "わざと雷を受けるなんて無茶はみんな、\nやめてくださいね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01636",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "わ、分かったわ……\nごめんなさい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01637",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "うちの愚妹が申し訳ない……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_01638",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "はぁ、それにしても結局ヘルトと戦うんだもんなぁ。\n……動きに気を付けないと……いざとなれば……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_01639",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]